# Environment Variables — {{app_name}}

Copy these into your `.env.local` file and fill in the values.

```env
# Supabase
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key

# LLM Providers
{{#each providers_display}}
{{#if (eq this.id "openai")}}
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-key
{{/if}}
{{#if (eq this.id "anthropic")}}
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-anthropic-key
{{/if}}
{{#if (eq this.id "google")}}
GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=your-google-ai-key
{{/if}}
{{/each}}

# App
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME={{app_name}}
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

## Where to Find These Values

| Variable | Where to find it |
|---|---|
| `SUPABASE_URL` | Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API → Project URL |
| `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` | Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API → `anon` `public` key |
| `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` | Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API → `service_role` key (keep secret!) |
{{#each providers_display}}
{{#if (eq this.id "openai")}}
| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | https://platform.openai.com/api-keys |
{{/if}}
